about.summary: Basic immutable container types for Python.

name: itypes
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "itypes" %}
{% set version = "1.1.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "c6e77bb9fd68a4bfeb9d958fea421802282451a25bac4913ec94db82a899c073" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - itypes

about:
  home: https://github.com/tomchristie/itypes
  license: BSD
  license_family: BSD
  # No license provided, though setup.py lists as BSD. Issue opened on repo
  #license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Basic immutable container types for Python.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - scopatz
